2: Modify the Password File to Gain the Root Privilege
We create a new account called charlie, and we will turn this normal
user into root using the Dirty COW attack. Adding a new account can be
achieved using the adduser command. After the account is created, a new
record will be added to /etc/passwd. See the following

The main thread #include &lt;fcntl.h&gt;
